title: Spintires v1.0.Build.09.11.2015-Tenguken
description:
Spintires (c) Oovee Game Studios

Release Date : 12/2015
Protection : Steam
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure, Simulation, Driving
Game Version : 1.0 Build 09.11.2015
Languages : EN/FR/DE/IT/ES/PL/CZ/HU/NL/JP/PT/DK/FI/GR/NO/SE/TR/RU

Take responsibility of operating large all-terrain Soviet vehicles
and venture across the rugged landscapes with only a map and compass
to guide you. Explore the levels and unlock portions of the map
whilst discovering new trucks, fuelling stations, garages and
lumber mills.

1. Burn or mount
2. Run setup.exe and install
3. Play
